description.plain: Nehemiah Lamar Harden (b. October 19, 2001), better known by his stage name SpotEmGottem, is an American rapper and songwriter. He is best known for his 2020 single “Beat Box”, which peaked at number 12 on the Billboard Hot 100.

songs.title: Beat Box

description.plain: Beat Box is a song by upcoming Florida rapper SpotemGottem it first gained fame on the app TikTok along with Beat Box 2, released on April 20, 2020. Months after its release, the rapper released his album Final Destination, which included a remix of the song featuring vocals by American rapper Pooh Shiesty named Beat Box 2. Since then, the song has been going viral on platforms such as TikTok and has led to the creation of many more remixes of the song featuring artists DaBaby, Latto, Shenseea, NLE Choppa and Polo G.

songs.title: Beat Box 3

description.plain:
One week after the release of DaBaby’s popular “Beatbox Freestyle” on YouTube, SpotEmGottem incorporated DaBaby’s verse into his original song to form “Beat Box 3.”

This marks the second “Beat Box” remix following Pooh Shiesty’s rendition on the viral “Beat Box 2.” The cover art flips that of SpotEmGottem’s album, Final Destination.
